Rating: 3
This was absolutely delicious and a crowd pleaser. I made this for a "stuffed appetizer" theme party. It was a big hit and received high marks for creativity. The accompanying sauce is delicious as well. A hint: if you have sensitive skin, wear plastic gloves when preparing the jalepenos; especially if you will be removing your contact lenses anytime soon after preparing this dish.